item.title: About me
item.author: juliana.spector@water.ca.gov (Juliana Spector)
item.description: I am an Engineering Geologist at the Department of Water Resources based in Sacramento, California. Outside of work, I enjoy singing in choir, rock climbing, and backpacking in the Sierras.
